text.tspan: 4.1 The Buyer requests access to digital content on the Seller's Website. The Seller
requests a Payment Token for the Buyer for the requested resource.
4.2 The Payswarm Authority knows that the Buyer had purchased the resource
previously. The previous Contract and License is sent to the Seller instead
of a Payment Token. The Buyer is not double-charged and is seamlessly
allowed to access the digital content.
